@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xiqtdp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs((v1 + 0.14 / tmp + 0.78)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(v2) + ((v1 + 0.46 - v0 + 0.90) / v2))
    v1 = wp.cos((v2 + (v1 + 0.01 - tmp + 0.50)))
    v1 = 0.32
    v0 = (0.03 + (wp.cos(v0 + 0.14) - (v2 + 0.29 + v1 + 0.04)))
    v2 = wp.exp(((v2 + 0.48 / tmp + 0.87) + v1))
    data[tid] = v0
